#: ../../source/recipes/uniform_attention_models.rst:4
msgid "Uniform Attention Models"
msgstr "Uniform Attention 模型"

#: ../../source/recipes/uniform_attention_models.rst:6
msgid ""
"Recipes for standard (uniform) attention transformer architectures "
"validated end-to-end with LMCache, with a recipe page per architecture "
"covering only the LMCache-specific configuration that diverges from "
"defaults."
msgstr "针对采用标准（uniform）attention 的 Transformer 架构的配方，均已通过 LMCache 端到端验证；每种架构对应一个配方页面，仅涵盖与默认配置不同的 LMCache 专项配置。"

#: ../../source/recipes/uniform_attention_models.rst:10
msgid ""
"These models use a **single attention type** across all layers, so vLLM "
"serves them with one KV cache group. Models that interleave multiple "
"attention types (sliding-window + full, or Mamba / linear-attention + "
"full) are covered under :doc:`/mp/hybrid_models`."
msgstr "这些模型在所有层中使用 **单一注意力类型**\\ ，因此 vLLM 使用一个 KV 缓存组为其提供服务。交错使用多种注意力类型的模型（sliding window attention + full attention，或 Mamba / linear attention + full attention）请参见 :doc:`/mp/hybrid_models`。"

#: ../../source/recipes/uniform_attention_models.rst:16
msgid "Recipe page contents"
msgstr "配方页面内容"

#: ../../source/recipes/uniform_attention_models.rst:18
msgid "Each recipe page is intentionally minimal:"
msgstr "每个配方页面均刻意保持简洁："

#: ../../source/recipes/uniform_attention_models.rst:20
msgid "**Validated models** -- exact HF repo IDs that have been tested."
msgstr "**验证过的模型** -- 已测试的确切 HF 仓库 ID。"

#: ../../source/recipes/uniform_attention_models.rst:21
msgid ""
"**Engine tabs** -- one tab per serving engine (vLLM, SGLang, TRT-LLM). "
"Each tab links to the engine's own documentation for the model and shows "
"the exact ``lmcache server`` and engine launch commands. Tabs for engines"
" that are not yet validated state so explicitly."
msgstr "**引擎选项卡** -- 每个推理引擎（vLLM、SGLang、TRT-LLM）各对应一个选项卡。每个选项卡链接至该引擎的模型文档，并给出 ``lmcache server`` 和引擎启动命令的完整示例。尚未完成验证的引擎会在选项卡中明确说明。"

#: ../../source/recipes/uniform_attention_models.rst:25
msgid "**CacheBlend support** -- validation status (may be empty)."
msgstr "**CacheBlend 支持** -- 验证状态（可能为空）。"

#: ../../source/recipes/uniform_attention_models.rst:26
msgid ""
"**Compression support** -- table of compression methods (CacheGen, etc.) "
"with per-method validation status. Extensible: new methods get a row."
msgstr "**压缩支持** -- 列出各压缩方法（CacheGen 等）及其验证状态的表格，支持扩展：新方法可直接新增一行。"

#: ../../source/recipes/uniform_attention_models.rst:28
msgid "**Caveats** -- known limitations, if any."
msgstr "**注意事项** -- 已知的限制（如果有的话）。"

#: ../../source/recipes/uniform_attention_models.rst:30
msgid ""
"For the generic LMCache + engine wiring (ports, remote hosts, sending a "
"first request), see :doc:`../getting_started/quickstart`. Recipes assume "
"that page as a prerequisite."
msgstr "有关 LMCache 与推理引擎的通用接入配置（端口、远程主机、发送首个请求），请参见 :doc:`../getting_started/quickstart`。本节配方均以该页面为前置阅读。"

